``k'' commentary news file.)  
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; IT'S TIME JAPAN DOES MORE THAN DUCK BEHIND THE SANDBAGS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-MILITARIZE-JAPAN-ECONOMIST-NYTSF......1,050 words &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ON YOUR MARK, NIGERIA: IF NEW START ISN'T GOOD, YOU'RE
FINISHED &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors...NOTE THIS WEEKEND'S ELECTION) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-NIGERIA-ON-TRACK?-ECONOMIST-NYTSF......800 words &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; `OR ELSE': WEST CRIES WOLF; SERBS OUTFOX BOMBERS _ FOR NOW &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-KOSOVO-ON-HOLD-ECONOMIST-NYTSF......725 words &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; EUROPE'S LATEST COUTURE: A FISCAL STRAITJACKET &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-TROUBLE-IN-EUROLAND-ECONOMIST-NYTSF......825 words &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; USA &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
