Fisher.
</P>
<P>
   ARGENTINA-POLITICS (Buenos Aires) _ Seven months after he
announced he was leaving office, President Carlos Saul Menem has
expressed interest in running for re-election if his supporters can
legally overturn a constitutional ban prohibiting a third
consecutive term. By Clifford Krauss.
</P>
<P>
