Francisco, had it tailored to fit, and was so pleased that she let
the store take a picture of her in it to use in a bus-shelter ad.
 &UR; _ Queen Elizabeth  &LR; has agreed to pose for  &UR; Lucien Freud &LR; , whose
portraits usually depict fleshy aging subjects in the nude.
</P>
<P>
   - If you're invited to Camp David for the weekend, you can't
exactly walk in empty-handed. If you're in the socks business, you
bring socks. And  &UR; Harvey Weinstein &LR;  of Miramax, who went there
recently, brought half a dozen movies, reports the New York
Observer.
</P>
