is asking $15,000 for a toupee once worn by  &UR; Frank &LR; 
 &UR; Sinatra &LR; . This item was in the possession of Sinatra's hairpiece
designer _ maybe it had been brought in for a tuneup _ and, for the
information of those in need of a match, is grayish white.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; - Michael Jackson &LR; , whose career has pretty much gone nowhere
since he was accused of playing well with children, is going to
make a comeback album for the millennium, says MSNBC.
</P>
<P>
   - The producers of ``Baywatch,'' hoping to move the series'
location to the Australian beach town of Avalon, changed plans
after a thousand residents _ a fifth of the population _ turned out
at a town meeting to say heck, no. Two episodes shot in Avalon this
