   WEAPONS-POLL (Undated ) _ If Kansas Citians have their way,
Missouri won't pass a concealed weapons law any time soon,
according to a poll by The Kansas City Star. By KIT WAGAR. Will
move in ``a'' category.
</P>
<P>
   BOOKBINDER-KANSAS (Selden, Kan.) _ The biggest business in tiny
Selden, Kan., is Koerperich Bookbinders, one of only 34 such
enterprises in the nation certified by the American Library
Association. By JIM FISHER. Will move in ``a'' category.
</P>
</TEXT>
